text: Raymond C. Setlakwe, (3 July 1928 – 14 October 2021) was a Canadian businessman, lawyer and Liberal politician. Setlakwe was born in Thetford Mines, Quebec, Canada. He was a member of the Senate of Canada between 2000 until 2003. Setlakwe died on 14 October 2021, aged 93.Décès de Raymond Setlakwe ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Canadian businesspeople Category:Canadian lawyers Category:Politicians from Quebec
